Package org.vast.ogc.om

Class ProcedureXML

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vast.ogc.om.ProcedureXML
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, AbstractFeature, AbstractGML, GenericFeature, IFeature, IProcedure, IResource
    public class ProcedureXML
extends java.lang.Object
implements IProcedure, GenericFeature

    Wrapper class to store procedure info as XML DOM. It can temporary hold a DOM Node until it is parsed by an adequate reader into a fully functional Procedure object.

    Since:
    Sep 30, 2012
